# ADR-016 — build-time SHA stamp (gitignored to prevent perpetual working-tree drift)
# Regenerated on prebuild / predev / npm run check via scripts/stamp-build-info.mjs
src/lib/build-info.ts

# Screenshots dropped in the repo root — Arc Search, macOS Cmd+Shift+3/4, etc.
# Stops accidental commits from blocking ship-merge's clean-tree guard
# (which refuses to merge if the working tree has anything modified/untracked).
Screenshot*
Screen Shot*
